Gayunpaman, palagi naming ginagamit

00:35:04.440 --> 00:35:05.740
Kodigo ni G. Hashimoto.

00:35:10.030 --> 00:35:11.420
Narito na ang iyong workstation.

00:35:12.150 --> 00:35:13.570
Ang pinuno ng iyong decryption team

00:35:13.590 --> 00:35:14.490
hindi pa dumarating.

