Commissioner Gu,

00:35:27.920 --> 00:35:28.940
diba sabi mo kanina

00:35:28.960 --> 00:35:31.220
may
ibibigay ka ba kay Major General Sasaki?

00:35:32.630 --> 00:35:33.420
Walang pagmamadali.

